            "name": "Howl of the Wild pg. 190",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "Howl of the Wild",
          "page": 190,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "The death of a unicorn in a particularly cruel manner leads to the creation of a pale horse\u2014a symbol of hope and purity transformed into one of hopelessness and despair.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
